          <list id="id1168943896164" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-roman" mark-prefix="(" mark-suffix=")">
            <item>Stem jy saam met die uitdrukking wat sê “Ghoema is Woema”. Motiveer.</item>
          </list>
          <para id="id1168939941471"/>
          <list id="id1168942881566" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-roman" mark-prefix="(" mark-suffix=")">
